# The Organisation tier's own address. Until the merchant tools ship there is
# no separate console to serve, so it lands on the main site rather than
# failing to resolve. Host rules must precede the SPA fallback below, and this
# only takes effect once org.trolleyscout.co.za is attached to the Pages
# project as a custom domain.
https://org.trolleyscout.co.za/*    https://trolleyscout.co.za/    302

# SPA fallback: deep links to client-side views (/deals, /near-me, …) serve the
# app shell with a 200 so they are crawlable and shareable. Pages Functions
# (/, /api/*, /mcp) and real static files are matched first and are unaffected.
/*    /index.html   200
